gtkdateentry
------------------------------------------
Gtk+ widget that semplifies date input.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.87.0-1
  libgtk2.0-devel-2.24.33-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.24.33-1
  libgtkdateentry-devel-0.0.2-1bl6
  libgtkdateentry0-0.0.2-1bl6
  libgtkmaskedentry-devel-0.0.2-1bl6
  libgtkmaskedentry0-0.0.2-1bl6
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.87.0-1
  libgtk2.0-devel-2.24.33-1
  libgtkmaskedentry-devel-0.0.2-1bl6
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtkdateentry/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/gtkdateentry/gtkdateentry-0.0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gtkdateentry-0.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gtkdateentry-0.0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gtkdateentry-0.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gtkdateentry-0.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgtkdateentry0-0.0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgtkdateentry-devel-0.0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gtkdateentry)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gtkdateentry.README
  /usr/share/doc/gtkdateentry/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/gtkdateentry/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/gtkdateentry/ChangeLog

(libgtkdateentry0)
  /usr/bin/cyggtkdateentry-0.dll

(libgtkdateentry-devel)
  /usr/include/gtkdateentry.h
  /usr/lib/libgtkdateentry.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libgtkdateentry.pc

